de.tudarmstadt.ukp.clarin.webanno.brat.curation

Class CasDiff

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.clarin.webanno.brat.curation.CasDiff

  • public class CasDiff
extends Object
    Class for finding clusters of equal annotations. Equal annotations are grouped into a AnnotationSelection. Instances of AnnotationSelection, which are exchangeble, because they refer to the same annotated unit, are grouped together in an AnnotationOption.
    Author:
    Andreas Straninger
